<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Appsmith | Open-Source Low-Code Application Platform</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Build the next generation of innovative, accurate, and secure enterprise applications with the leader in open-source low-code development.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-container">
        <a href="/" class="logo">Appsmith</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/sign-up">Sign Up</a>
          <a href="/getting-started/setup">Setup</a>
          <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Deliver custom AI-powered apps and agents faster</h1>
          <p class="hero-description">Build the next generation of innovative, accurate, and secure enterprise applications with the leader in open-source low-code development.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="https://www.appsmith.com/" class="btn btn-primary">Start for free</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Get a demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="feature-intro">
          <h2>Build custom AI apps 80% faster</h2>
          <p>Connect to LLMs, applications, and databases. Use built-in AI actions. Prompt or drag-and-drop UI components. Customize logic with JS. Manage and maintain with Git. Appsmith makes it easy to build any application.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558494949-ef010cbdcc31?w=48&h=48&fit=crop" alt="Connect icon">
            </div>
            <h3>Connect</h3>
            <p>Interact with any LLM, database, SaaS tool or REST/GraphQL API. Self host for secure access to internal data.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581291518633-83b4ebd1d83e?w=48&h=48&fit=crop" alt="Build icon">
            </div>
            <h3>Build</h3>
            <p>Use drag-and-drop widgets to quickly assemble responsive UI. Prompt your own widgets in natural language, or code them in JS/HTML/CSS.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517077304055-6e89abbf09b0?w=48&h=48&fit=crop" alt="Customize icon">
            </div>
            <h3>Customize</h3>
            <p>Automate workflows, manipulate appearance, and transform data with JS code or natural language prompts. Import your own JS libraries.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556075798-4825dfaaf498?w=48&h=48&fit=crop" alt="Deploy icon">
            </div>
            <h3>Deploy and maintain</h3>
            <p>Version control and merge updates with Git. Automatically deploy merged changes from designated environment branches.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="explore-cta">
          <a href="https://www.appsmith.com/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore the product</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="social-proof">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Leading companies are innovating with Appsmith</h2>
        <p>From startups to enterprises, businesses are improving operations and increasing efficiency by building custom apps on Appsmith.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <blockquote>Reduce seat licenses</blockquote>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=400&h=200&fit=crop" alt="F22 Labs testimonial">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="g2-badges">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Appsmith is a leader in digital process automation and low-code development</h2>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=800&h=300&fit=crop" alt="G2 badges">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="developer-first">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="content-text">
            <h2>Developer-first low-code development</h2>
            <p>Whether you're prompting or coding, Appsmith offers full transparency and code-level control over every aspect of application development.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="content-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Developer-first platform">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="enterprise-features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Enterprise scale security, and governance</h2>
        <p>Deliver custom software lightning-fast with the user and access controls, compliance, uptime, and deployment options required for enterprise teams.</p>
        
        <div class="enterprise-grid">
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563986768494-4dee2763ff3f?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Self-hosting">
            <h3>Self-hosting with air-gapped deployment options</h3>
            <p>Run any edition of Appsmith in your infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551434678-e076c223a692?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Embeddable">
            <h3>Embeddable within existing apps with shared logins</h3>
            <p>Extend the functionality of your legacy and SaaS applications.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517077304055-6e89abbf09b0?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Open source">
            <h3>Open source under Apache 2.0 license</h3>
            <p>Build with high transparency and low vendor risk.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="SAML SSO">
            <h3>SAML and OIDC SSO</h3>
            <p>Secure authentication and authorization with your login provider.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553028826-f4804a6dfd3f?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="RBAC">
            <h3>Role-based access controls</h3>
            <p>Customize granular roles, groups, and permissions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556075798-4825dfaaf498?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="SCIM">
            <h3>SCIM-based user provisioning</h3>
            <p>Import users and roles from your IdP.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586281380349-632531db7ed4?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Audit logging">
            <h3>Audit logging</h3>
            <p>Track organizational use and remediate issues.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563986768494-4dee2763ff3f?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="SOC 2">
            <h3>SOC 2 Type II</h3>
            <p>Proven security processes and controls.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="enterprise-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553484771-371a605b060b?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Support">
            <h3>Award-winning support</h3>
            <p>Development and deployment assistance with rapid response SLAs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Appsmith is lightweight, fast, and developer-focused. It's easy to get started.</h2>
        <a href="https://login.appsmith.com/" class="btn btn-primary">Get started for free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Appsmith. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand: #6366f1;
      --brand-alt: #8b5cf6;
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --surface: #f8fafc;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --muted: #64748b;
      
      --font-heading: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      
      --space-0: 0px;
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-7: 32px;
      --space-8: 40px;
      --space-9: 48px;
      --space-10: 64px;
      --space-11: 80px;
      --space-12: 96px;
      
      --radius-sm: 4px;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    }

    header {
      background: var(--bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      height: var(--space-10);
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-7);
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--brand);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--brand-alt);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: var(--muted);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--brand);
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .features {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    }

    .feature-intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }

    .feature-intro h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-8);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-7);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: var(--space-9);
      height: var(--space-9);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .feature-icon img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .explore-cta {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .social-proof {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      background: var(--surface);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .social-proof h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-8);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .g2-badges {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .g2-badges h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }

    .g2-badges img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    }

    .developer-first {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content-text h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .content-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .enterprise-features {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    }

    .enterprise-features h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .enterprise-features > p {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
    }

    .enterprise-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .enterprise-item {
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface);
    }

    .enterprise-item img {
      width: var(--space-10);
      height: var(--space-10);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .enterprise-item h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .cta {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      background: var(--surface);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--text);
      color: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-8) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        gap: var(--space-4);
      }
      
      .hero-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .enterprise-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>